item.title: Almost done but
item.dc:creator: @mail1 mail`
item.description:
@mail1 wrote:

Ah i see, right then to host with hamachi you must.

Step one.
Make sevral hamachi networks.

Step two.
Look at the top of your hamachi, you will see a number like 5.67.22.94 ( of course yours will be differnt! :P) This is the IP address people will use to get onto your server.

Step three.
You must compile and run your server while in hamachi, people can only get on to it if it is running. Either by compile.bat / runserver.bat.

That should cover it, need any more help ? just ask
